If you believe you are or will be a qualifying veteran, contact your financial aid office and provide a copy of your DD214 (military separation form). If you are not and will not be a veteran, you must change the answer to Item 46 from "Yes" to "No" and provide parental information, including the signature of at least one of your parents.
